Package: shinyAntDesignX
Title: Ant Design X AI Chat UI for Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kaiping", "Yang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "kaiping.yang@example.com")
Description: A collection of Shiny htmlwidgets wrapping Ant Design X React components.
    Provides component-based widgets: streaming Markdown (XMarkdown), syntax-highlighted
    code (CodeHighlighter), Mermaid diagrams, tool call chain visualization (ThoughtChain),
    and a full AI chat interface with streaming, tool calls, and conversation history.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
